title: EU, Canada sign historic CETA free trade agreement
description:
After seven years of negotiations the European Union and Canada signed the Comprehensive Economic & Trade Agreement (CETA) in Brussels, Belgium. The deal eliminates 99 percent of tariffs between the EU and Canada. RT correspondent Alex Mihailovich joins RT America’s Simone Del Rosario to break down the deal.
